movie.title: No Such Thing As Monsters
movie.description_intro: A young couple on a romantic weekend in the Australian bush are terrorised by a psychopathic family.
movie.description_full: A young couple on a romantic weekend in the Australian bush are terrorised by a psychopathic family.

movies.title: Barricade
movies.summary: This movie is about the Shade family, a year after the death of the mother/wife Leah, the husband and father (Eric McCormack) and his two children go to a cabin retreat in the mountains. While there they are tormented by visions and happenings that start to scare them. But are these incidents real or in their minds? The father feels compelled to barricade them in the cabin in order to keep them safe. But will it work out?

movies.title: How to Train Your Dragon
movies.summary: Long ago up North on the Island of Berk, the young Viking, Hiccup, wants to join his town's fight against the dragons that continually raid their town. However, his macho father and village leader, Stoik the Vast, will not allow his small, clumsy, but inventive son to do so. Regardless, Hiccup ventures out into battle and downs a mysterious Night Fury dragon with his invention, but can't bring himself to kill it. Instead, Hiccup and the dragon, whom he dubs Toothless, begin a friendship that would open up both their worlds as the observant boy learns that his people have misjudged the species. But even as the two each take flight in their own way, they find that they must fight the destructive ignorance plaguing their world.

movies.title: Escaping My Stalker
movies.summary: A street kid, Taylor (Ezmie Garcia), has been adopted by Sandy (Alexandra Paul) & Larry (Linden Ashby). They run a shelter for people in need, and rescued Taylor from the street, and a life of crime. Unfortunately, Taylor's past may be catching up with her. She's got a stalker, and he means business. Can she figure out who's behind this, and why before her new life is snatched away?

movies.title: Return of the Living Dead III
movies.title_english: Return of the Living Dead III
movies.title_long: Return of the Living Dead III (1993)
movies.summary: Colonel Reynolds and his group of government scientists continue their work on re-animating the dead for military use. His son Curt and his girlfriend Julie use Dad's security pass to sneak in and watch the proceedings. Later when father and son have a disagreement, Curt and Julie take off on a motorcycle and Julie is killed in an accident. Grief-stricken, Curt takes her body to the lab and brings her back to life. Curt must help Julie deal with her new existence as military agents and local gang members try to find them.
